  <brief_title>Hyperbaric Oxygen Treatment as Adjuvant Treatment for Frost Injury</brief_title>
  <acronym>FROST</acronym>
  <official_title>Study of the Possible Improvement in Level of Sequela and Amputation/Amputation Level After Frost Injury by the Adjuvant Treatment of Hyperbaric Oxygen.</official_title>
