  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-70. Frost damage grade II-IV. Inclusion is needed within 48 hours from time of
             damage.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy. Ventilator treatment. Problems with equalizing. High grade heart failure.
             Chronic obstructive lung disease of high grade. Treatment over 3 days after time of
             damage. Serious claustrophobia/psychiatric illness.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
